msgid "{i0}{item} {i6} put inside {name}'s bag."
msgstr "{i0}{item}{i6}放到了{name}的包里。"

#. BATTLE_MSG_PRESENT_FULL
msgid "But you can't carry any more stuff..."
msgstr "但是你不能再携带更多物品了......"

